overview:
An effective Small Business Advisory Board and Executive Business Coach summary is a two to three page document that details your company’s vision statement, mission statement, goals, objectives, core projects, target customers/clients and value proposition.

The Alternative Board establishes your own board of advisors and small business mentor. Thousands of business owners of small- and medium-sized companies are members of TAB boards. There are over 140 TAB franchises operating in five countries.
